parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake vacuum pump can cause the brakes to fail, leading to loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The "Braking Power Low" or "Low Brake Power" warning message appears on the dashboard
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to stop or slow down.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the sunroof can cause injury to occupants, distraction to the driver, and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: Loud explosion or banging sound
shattered sunroof glass
and in some cases
no apparent reason or object that caused the shattering.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can lead to loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake pedal sticks to the floor
"Brake" light on the dash
and "Braking Power Low" warning message.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch system can cause difficulty shifting gears, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
clutch pedal sticks to the floor
and difficulty shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the blind spot monitoring system can increase the risk of accidents, as drivers may not be aware of vehicles in their blind spot.
symptoms: Intermittent detection of vehicles
failure to detect large vehicles
and inconsistent performance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the pre-collision system can increase the risk of accidents, as drivers may not receive warnings or assistance in avoiding collisions.
symptoms: False or unnecessary warnings
failure to detect potential collisions
and inconsistent performance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of Bluetooth connectivity can distract drivers and decrease the safety of hands-free features.
symptoms: Intermittent or complete loss of Bluetooth connectivity
inability to use hands-free features.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The presence of a musty smell and water ingress can lead to mold growth, decreased air quality, and potentially cause health issues.
symptoms: Musty smell
water found under passenger carpet
and mold growth.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unusual noises and potential cybersecurity concerns can distract drivers and decrease the safety of the vehicle.
symptoms: Loud buzzing sound
unusual noise
and concerns about cybersecurity.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, compromising the safety of vehicle occupants.
symptoms: Airbags did not deploy in a crash
despite the severity of the impact; no warning lights or indicators were present; occupants suffered injuries or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Vehicle accelerated suddenly and uncontrollably; brake pedal did not respond or was stuck; vehicle sped off without driver input; near-miss or actual collision occurred.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty SRS airbag system can lead to airbag failure, compromising vehicle safety.
symptoms: SRS airbag warning indicator illuminated on the dashboard; dealership diagnosed a wiring harness issue; repair estimate was high
and the part was no longer under warranty.
